snippet.title: Star Ranger - Commodore 64
snippet.description:
Commodore 64 cartridge game - "Star Ranger"
The game was released in 1983 by Commodore Business Machines
After having not played this game for probably 20 years, this is my "walkthrough" of the stages of Level 1. Not my best attempt, but you get to see all the stages completed.... eventually.
